    <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Last month we introduced &lt;a href="http://www.projectatomic.io/blog/2016/05/introducing_commissaire/"&gt;Commissaire&lt;/a&gt;
giving a quick overview of features and architecture.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This month we wanted to show how one can:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run a Commissaire server&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Configure commctl for use with Commissaire&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create a new cluster via commctl&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bootstrap a new host node via commctl&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;ssh to a host node via commctl&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

